WEBVTT

00:00:04.480 --> 00:00:06.789
Good evening,

00:00:06.799 --> 00:00:08.549
family. Thank you for joining me again

00:00:08.559 --> 00:00:10.310
tonight. I got around a little later

00:00:10.320 --> 00:00:13.110
because we went to church, and I

00:00:13.120 --> 00:00:15.030
was rushing to feed the kids and stuff

00:00:15.040 --> 00:00:18.870
before, and I apologize. I want to get on here earlier because there are so many of you that say, "Hey, I go to bed. What? You're praying way too late, Brandon."And I would love it. I think I'm trying to start to get the live streams around 7:00, but that'll affect going to Wednesday night church and stuff. I don't know what we're going to do. But I know in my heart when I do the live streams around 7:00, we'll get over 10,000 people on a live stream at one time. And so, I believe that's significant for prayer results. You know, we're touching the nations. I believe with all my heart we're touching the nations for Jesus. And people are getting saved, and it's just wonderful what God is doing

00:00:18.870 --> 00:00:18.880
here. So, I just want

00:00:18.880 --> 00:00:20.710
to be encouraging tonight about some

00:00:20.720 --> 00:00:23.109
of the things that the Lord was—we were

00:00:23.119 --> 00:00:27.349
praying over last night. Whenever the

00:00:27.359 --> 00:00:30.230
spirit of the Lord hit my little girl

00:00:30.240 --> 00:00:33.190
in that river as she was

00:00:33.200 --> 00:00:36.229
interceding for me, interceding

00:00:36.239 --> 00:00:38.709
with Diana, and they were praying,

00:00:38.719 --> 00:00:40.389
everybody kept saying, "I hear a third

00:00:40.389 --> 00:00:40.399
voice."We

00:00:40.399 --> 00:00:42.630
don't know who the third voice

00:00:42.640 --> 00:00:45.430
was. I kept thinking it was Sister

00:00:45.430 --> 00:00:45.440
Billie.

00:00:45.440 --> 00:00:48.709
I told Diana I thought she was

00:00:48.719 --> 00:00:50.950
playing something and they were

00:00:50.960 --> 00:00:53.189
praying alongside it, but there was

00:00:53.199 --> 00:00:54.950
nobody else in the house. They were in

00:00:54.960 --> 00:00:58.150
the closet and they were praying, and it

00:00:58.160 --> 00:01:00.630
was so loud in the closet that it

00:01:00.640 --> 00:01:02.630
sounded like a third person was praying

00:01:02.640 --> 00:01:04.710
with them, but there was not a third

00:01:04.720 --> 00:01:07.510
person. So, I thought it was really

00:01:07.520 --> 00:01:11.510
interesting because I even

00:01:11.520 --> 00:01:12.870
personally thought there was a third

00:01:12.880 --> 00:01:15.350
person. And I kept thinking, and I told

00:01:15.360 --> 00:01:17.910
Diana, I said, "That sounds familiar.

00:01:17.920 --> 00:01:20.710
Who is that?"And I was trying to

00:01:20.720 --> 00:01:22.390
figure it out myself. Diana said, "There

00:01:22.400 --> 00:01:25.270
was nobody in the closet with

00:01:25.280 --> 00:01:27.510
us."So,

00:01:27.520 --> 00:01:29.270
we tried to think about that. We thought

00:01:29.280 --> 00:01:31.830
about that all the rest of the night.

00:01:31.840 --> 00:01:34.390
Who was the third voice

00:01:34.400 --> 00:01:37.510
praying and interceding? It was loud.

00:01:37.520 --> 00:01:39.030
But it was interesting because so many

00:01:39.040 --> 00:01:41.670
of you heard the third voice, too. And

00:01:41.680 --> 00:01:44.149
Paisley was praying. What we were

00:01:44.159 --> 00:01:47.910
praying about, we saw great revival

00:01:47.920 --> 00:01:52.069
coming to the nation, but it was with

00:01:52.079 --> 00:01:56.789
the youth. I saw a stirring in the youth

00:01:56.799 --> 00:01:59.910
that was all over Australia, all over

00:01:59.920 --> 00:02:03.429
America, Europe, but God was touching the

00:02:03.439 --> 00:02:07.429
young people in a glorious way.

00:02:10.160 --> 00:02:13.830
In a glorious way that was

00:02:13.840 --> 00:02:16.470
over the top of anything I could dare

00:02:16.480 --> 00:02:18.710
ask or think concerning the youth. The

00:02:18.720 --> 00:02:21.190
Lord said, "The devil has come after the

00:02:21.200 --> 00:02:22.949
youth hard, but I'm coming after him

00:02:22.949 --> 00:02:22.959
harder."Brandon,

00:02:22.959 --> 00:02:26.070
there will be—and I saw

00:02:26.080 --> 00:02:29.030
at the Church of His Presence,

00:02:29.040 --> 00:02:31.910
I saw a major youth revival

00:02:31.920 --> 00:02:35.270
also taking place with the glorious

00:02:35.280 --> 00:02:37.270
outpouring that's going to take

00:02:37.280 --> 00:02:39.270
place there. And then that was the

00:02:39.280 --> 00:02:40.630
same thing the Lord was talking to us

00:02:40.640 --> 00:02:43.030
about the youth building that the

00:02:43.040 --> 00:02:45.350
church in Collinsville is building and

00:02:45.360 --> 00:02:48.229
what God is going to do with the

00:02:48.239 --> 00:02:51.190
outpouring of the spirit on the youth in

00:02:51.200 --> 00:02:54.710
Oklahoma. I know in my heart,

00:02:54.720 --> 00:02:57.589
just as Paisley was praying and

00:02:57.599 --> 00:03:01.910
interceding for the youth and

00:03:01.910 --> 00:03:01.920
for me—I

00:03:01.920 --> 00:03:03.670
mean for the

00:03:03.670 --> 00:03:03.680
broadcast—it

00:03:03.680 --> 00:03:07.030
was just over the top because

00:03:07.040 --> 00:03:10.470
she was in

00:03:10.480 --> 00:03:12.869
that travail, as you know. And everybody

00:03:12.869 --> 00:03:12.879
asks,

00:03:12.879 --> 00:03:14.390
"How old is Paisley?"I don't let

00:03:14.400 --> 00:03:16.070
Paisley come on the internet. She's my

00:03:16.080 --> 00:03:18.790
youngest, and she is

00:03:18.790 --> 00:03:18.800
just—she's

00:03:18.800 --> 00:03:21.110
not even a teenager yet; she's

00:03:21.120 --> 00:03:24.229
just a child.

00:03:24.239 --> 00:03:27.750
And so, most people want to

00:03:27.750 --> 00:03:27.760
know—no,

00:03:27.760 --> 00:03:29.430
I've got a lot of creepy people that

00:03:29.440 --> 00:03:32.789
follow me, and I protect Paisley.

00:03:32.799 --> 00:03:34.869
There's a call on Paisley's life,

00:03:34.879 --> 00:03:37.270
and even with my other children

00:03:37.280 --> 00:03:40.470
as we all know, but Paisley is already

00:03:40.480 --> 00:03:42.710
seeing, and so we just don't talk about

00:03:42.720 --> 00:03:44.630
it. God's developing some things inside

00:03:44.640 --> 00:03:47.670
her, and it's through prayer.

00:03:47.680 --> 00:03:50.309
I teach her everything I know;

00:03:50.319 --> 00:03:52.390
we pray in the car together, and I'm

00:03:52.400 --> 00:03:54.949
teaching her even before she becomes

00:03:54.959 --> 00:03:58.229
a teenager how to jump in these rivers

00:03:58.239 --> 00:04:01.110
and see prophetically and be

00:04:01.120 --> 00:04:04.390
yielded to it. And so, it's been

00:04:04.400 --> 00:04:06.470
amazing to watch what he's done with

00:04:06.480 --> 00:04:09.429
this little girl. Braden is very

00:04:09.439 --> 00:04:12.229
techy and very smart like his mama. Diana

00:04:12.229 --> 00:04:12.239
is

00:04:12.239 --> 00:04:14.949
very smart, and they are

00:04:14.959 --> 00:04:16.949
able to do things that I can't do. So,

00:04:16.959 --> 00:04:20.069
it's very interesting how we all flow

00:04:20.079 --> 00:04:22.390
together with our giftings. Diana's

00:04:22.400 --> 00:04:24.950
really smart with finances and things

00:04:24.960 --> 00:04:26.310
like that, and Braden's smart with

00:04:26.320 --> 00:04:28.150
technological things. Paisley

00:04:28.150 --> 00:04:28.160
is

00:04:28.160 --> 00:04:29.670
still trying to figure out

00:04:29.680 --> 00:04:31.749
what God's called her to do, but I see

00:04:31.759 --> 00:04:35.510
more of a prayer mantle on her than

00:04:35.520 --> 00:04:37.909
any kid usually at her age.

00:04:37.919 --> 00:04:39.670
I've never seen it before. And I'm not

00:04:39.680 --> 00:04:41.749
bragging because she's my kid. You know,

00:04:41.749 --> 00:04:41.759
you'll

00:04:41.759 --> 00:04:43.189
go, "Well, yeah, of course you'd say

00:04:43.199 --> 00:04:45.030
that because that's your

00:04:45.030 --> 00:04:45.040
child."No,

00:04:45.040 --> 00:04:47.510
no, no. This is different. It's

00:04:47.520 --> 00:04:50.390
different. I know. And I'm one

00:04:50.400 --> 00:04:51.990
of those Simon Cowells. I'm not going to

00:04:52.000 --> 00:04:54.230
tell the person if their kid

00:04:54.240 --> 00:04:56.070
can't sing very well and they're in

00:04:56.080 --> 00:04:58.870
there auditioning for tryouts for

00:04:58.880 --> 00:05:00.550
singing, I'm going to say, "Honey, you

00:05:00.560 --> 00:05:02.710
just don't got it. It's okay. You can

00:05:02.720 --> 00:05:04.230
develop it or something through voice

00:05:04.230 --> 00:05:04.240
lessons."I'm

00:05:04.240 --> 00:05:07.843
just

00:05:07.853 --> 00:05:10.230
really blunt. And so,

00:05:10.240 --> 00:05:11.189
you know, that's why I believe that

00:05:11.199 --> 00:05:12.950
God's called me to go to certain places

00:05:12.960 --> 00:05:16.230
and rattle the places with the

00:05:16.240 --> 00:05:18.469
prophetic gifting inside of you. God

00:05:18.479 --> 00:05:21.670
calls you to stir churches; God calls

00:05:21.680 --> 00:05:24.310
you to stir the people. I have pastors

00:05:24.320 --> 00:05:26.070
from all around the world watch me and say,

00:05:26.070 --> 00:05:26.080
"Brandon,

00:05:26.080 --> 00:05:28.070
you're stirring us up to get

00:05:28.080 --> 00:05:30.790
us ready for the end times."My job is

00:05:30.800 --> 00:05:33.909
to rattle the cages, to yell from

00:05:33.919 --> 00:05:36.790
there. And I don't

00:05:36.800 --> 00:05:38.790
ever feel like I'm correcting; I'm just

00:05:38.800 --> 00:05:41.110
yelling through what the Lord is

00:05:41.120 --> 00:05:43.590
telling me to say to pastors, to

00:05:43.600 --> 00:05:46.469
churches, to ministries to warn you that

00:05:46.479 --> 00:05:48.790
he's coming. And we must give

00:05:48.790 --> 00:05:48.800
altar

00:05:48.800 --> 00:05:52.629
calls. We must get the lost saved. Even

00:05:52.639 --> 00:05:54.230
if you don't think anybody in your

00:05:54.240 --> 00:05:56.070
congregation is going to be saved that

00:05:56.080 --> 00:05:59.189
night, give people the opportunity to

00:05:59.199 --> 00:06:01.430
make a choice.

00:06:01.440 --> 00:06:03.029
And God's going to hold us accountable

00:06:03.039 --> 00:06:06.469
for it. And I'm so thankful that we're

00:06:06.479 --> 00:06:08.629
seeing that now. We're seeing some fruit

00:06:08.639 --> 00:06:10.550
of that. We're seeing some fruit and

00:06:10.560 --> 00:06:13.110
some change, and we're seeing God move

00:06:13.120 --> 00:06:15.749
on some hearts. And it's wonderful to

00:06:15.759 --> 00:06:19.189
see the opportunity for the lost to

00:06:19.199 --> 00:06:21.990
give their heart to Jesus Christ.

00:06:22.000 --> 00:06:24.710
So, my heart is souls; my heart is

00:06:24.710 --> 00:06:24.720
a

00:06:24.720 --> 00:06:26.790
passion for souls. And we're seeing

00:06:26.800 --> 00:06:29.110
so many saved on this channel. It's

00:06:29.120 --> 00:06:31.430
amazing to see what the Lord is doing in

00:06:31.440 --> 00:06:33.909
these last days. Either we believe that

00:06:33.919 --> 00:06:36.629
he's coming or we don't.

00:06:36.639 --> 00:06:39.350
Either we believe that the coming of the

00:06:39.360 --> 00:06:42.710
Lord is at hand or we don't. And if we

00:06:42.720 --> 00:06:45.590
do believe it, there'll be urgency

00:06:45.600 --> 00:06:49.670
behind what we say and how we act.

00:06:51.199 --> 00:06:53.990
Some of us are growing more than others.

00:06:54.000 --> 00:06:55.430
Some of us are going through the

00:06:55.440 --> 00:06:57.350
birthing pains of ministry that we've

00:06:57.360 --> 00:06:59.029
never walked before. And that's me and

00:06:59.039 --> 00:07:01.110
Diana. We've never walked this before.

00:07:01.120 --> 00:07:03.270
So, we try to find camaraderie in people

00:07:03.280 --> 00:07:05.990
sometimes, and maybe the Lord

00:07:06.000 --> 00:07:07.990
always said for us to stay to ourselves

00:07:08.000 --> 00:07:11.670
and we need to grow

00:07:11.680 --> 00:07:13.270
with our birthing pains a little bit

00:07:13.280 --> 00:07:15.670
more privately. But I'm going to tell

00:07:15.680 --> 00:07:19.990
you this, it's all been amazing what the

00:07:20.000 --> 00:07:23.110
Lord has done with us in the last two

00:07:23.120 --> 00:07:25.670
and a half years. And the Lord spoke to

00:07:25.680 --> 00:07:27.189
me today and he told me to tell you

00:07:27.199 --> 00:07:31.270
this. We were driving down the road

00:07:31.280 --> 00:07:34.070
and I was going to do some things

00:07:34.080 --> 00:07:36.710
with Diana,

00:07:36.720 --> 00:07:40.070
and I'm telling you, I was looking

00:07:40.080 --> 00:07:43.350
over at a tree as I was driving and I

00:07:43.360 --> 00:07:46.070
was in the spirit praying,

00:07:46.080 --> 00:07:48.070
and all of a sudden the Lord said, "I want

00:07:48.080 --> 00:07:50.790
to talk to you about what's coming

00:07:50.800 --> 00:07:54.070
as you see this shot that President

00:07:54.080 --> 00:07:55.990
Trump has in his hand right now."Do you

00:07:56.000 --> 00:07:59.830
see that? He's about to interject. He's

00:07:59.840 --> 00:08:02.390
about to

00:08:04.560 --> 00:08:06.309
administer

00:08:06.319 --> 00:08:08.950
