00:08:08.960 --> 00:08:09.990
Is that what a doctor does?

00:08:10.000 --> 00:08:10.790
Yeah,

00:08:10.800 --> 00:08:13.909
inject into the economy.

00:08:13.919 --> 00:08:16.070
He's about to show up and

00:08:16.080 --> 00:08:19.110
show off in a way the Lord is in your

00:08:19.120 --> 00:08:22.710
finances. And he said, "There'll be many

00:08:22.720 --> 00:08:25.029
of you."I want you to hear

00:08:25.039 --> 00:08:26.629
what he said. He said, "There'll be many

00:08:26.639 --> 00:08:30.469
of you that have had the opportunity and

00:08:30.479 --> 00:08:33.269
