00:08:36.550 --> 00:08:36.560
in

00:08:36.560 --> 00:08:39.509
a short amount of time—will have

00:08:39.519 --> 00:08:41.909
the wealth of what we talked about

00:08:41.909 --> 00:08:41.919
in

00:08:41.919 --> 00:08:44.470
Deuteronomy

00:08:44.470 --> 00:08:44.480
8:

00:08:44.480 --> 00:08:47.670
wells you didn't dig, houses you didn't

00:08:47.680 --> 00:08:49.190
furnish,

00:08:49.200 --> 00:08:51.990
blessing and increase beyond anything

00:08:52.000 --> 00:08:55.190
you can ever comprehend, imagine, or think

00:08:55.200 --> 00:08:57.829
is coming to you."And the Lord told me,

00:08:57.839 --> 00:09:00.389
'Brandon, I'm telling you, I'm going

00:09:00.399 --> 00:09:02.870
to show you today.'As I was driving, he

00:09:02.880 --> 00:09:05.829
said, 'I'm going to show you today. I show

00:09:05.839 --> 00:09:08.710
you a lot of the warnings

00:09:08.720 --> 00:09:12.230
on the other side of the coin, but I am

00:09:12.240 --> 00:09:14.949
going to allow you to see

00:09:14.959 --> 00:09:16.870
the blessing side

00:09:16.880 --> 00:09:20.870
right now privately between me and you,

00:09:20.880 --> 00:09:22.389
and you can tell the people what's

00:09:22.399 --> 00:09:23.990
coming.'As

00:09:24.000 --> 00:09:27.350
I was looking over, I saw that

00:09:27.360 --> 00:09:29.269
big thing.

00:09:29.279 --> 00:09:32.150
I saw great financial stimulation

